- Common Throwables
  -----------------

- CheckedExceptions:
IOException			// input-output failures
SOAPException		// SOAP based WS failures
SQLException		// SQL DB failures
URISyntaxException	// Malformed representation of the destination endpoint
XMLParseException	// XML Doc processing failures

- RuntimeExceptions:
ArithmeticException		// arithmetic failures (e.g: div by zero)
ArrayStoreException		// storage in array failures (invalid item)
ClassCastException		// casting failures
ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException	// access not-existing-items failures
NullPointerException	//	not initialized object failures

  - Errors:
1) AssertionError		// thrown by "assert" statement used by a senior Developer
2) OutOfMemoryError		// heap
3) StackOverflowError	// stack

assert x > 0;	// disabled by default. Requires execution with argument:
				// -ea or -enableassertions